🧠 Dopamine Bro (Prefrontal Lab)

"Master your dopamine. Reclaim your focus. Become the best version of yourself."

Dopamine Bro is your personal AI assistant for managing cognitive energy. We’ve turned neuroscience into RPG mechanics, allowing you to see in real-time how your daily decisions impact your brain's performance.
🚀 How It Works

We track your internal resources using two key metrics:

    Prefrontal Charge: Your reservoir of willpower, logic, and decision-making ability. When it hits zero, focusing on code becomes impossible.

    Limbic Heat: The activity level of your "inner beast." It rises from endless scrolling, sugar, and information noise. The higher the "heat," the harder it is to say "no" to bad habits.

🛠 Developer Features (The Engineer’s Edge)
⚡ Deep Work "ULTA" Mode

The "Ulta" (Ultimate) is your maximum productivity mode. It’s not just a timer—it’s a total system lockdown.

    Activation Cost: Requires Prefrontal Charge > 80%. You can't trigger your "Ulta" if you are cognitively depleted.

    System Lockdown: Automatic "whitelist" protocol.

        Desktop: Blocks all non-work domains (YouTube/Reddit/TG) via hosts file edits or browser extensions.

        Mobile: Enters "Nokia Mode"—only calls and IDE notifications are allowed.

    Flow State Protection: Automatically sets your status to ⛔ In the Zone in Slack/Discord and silences all notifications.

🔌 Automatic Integrations

No manual entry. We pull data from where you actually work:

    WakaTime / VS Code API: We track your "Coding Heat." Coded in Python for 2 hours? Prefrontal Charge +25%.

    GitHub API: Merged a PR? Dopamine Streak +1.

    Health Connect / Apple Health: Your sleep and steps are automatically converted into "charge" recovery.

🦾 Modes & States
Mode	Prefrontal Status	Limbic Heat	Restrictions
Nokia (Emergency)	Low (Power Save)	High	Calls, SMS, and Gallery only.
Blackberry (Work)	Balanced	Under Control	Slack, Email, Calendar, Music.
ULTA (Dev God)	Maximum	Zero	IDE and Documentation only. Hard Lock.
🧬 State Mathematics

Our goal is to keep the balance in favor of reason, not impulses. The algorithm calculates your efficiency using the formula:
Efficiency=LimbicHeatCodeCommitFrequency×PrefrontalCharge​
🗣 Bro-Notifications (The Honest Voice in Your Pocket)

The app won’t coddle you. It tells the raw truth:

    "Bro, you’ve been staring at the screen for 30 minutes and haven't done a thing. Your prefrontal cortex is fried. Go sleep or take a walk—right now, you’re just wasting time."

📥 Why This Works

Unlike "sterile" habit trackers, Dopamine Bro gives developers what they understand: numbers, logs, and results. It turns the struggle against dopamine addiction into a system optimization task.​
